text.tspan: The loan pays for all construction costs as well as production-
losses up front (prior to the start of construction) and is not due
until the company starts saving money from the waste heat
recycling equipment that was installed during construction.
Monthly loan repayment is structured so as to
be equivalent to the difference between the
company's old and new energy consumption
